The empty weight of the vehicle in kg as specified. For motor vehicles of class M1 registered up to December 31, 1996: Empty weight according to vehicle registration certificate or registration certificate Part I minus weight of tank contents at 90 percent filling. For motor vehicles of category M1 registered on or after January 1, 1997: Empty weight according to vehicle registration certificate or registration certificate Part I minus weight of tank contents at 90 percent filling and minus weight of driver (75 kg). For motor vehicles of class N1: empty weight according to the vehicle registration document or registration certificate Part I minus the weight of the tank contents with a 90 percent filling and minus the weight of the driver (75 kg).

vehicle variant - Body shapes: Sedan, station wagon, hatchback, coupe, convertible, SUV, pickup, Doka (double cab), etc. Also special models that may differ from the basic shapes (e.g. BMW M-series, Audi S-series, Long version, right-hand drive, special vehicles (armor). etc. ).
